        "TileImage": "$($repository 80051c02-e026-40fe-970a-7b7aaa62302c).Image",
        "Description": "Hello, 47.\rMumbai has become the stage for a carefully borrowed identity. Four targets have been marked for elimination. You will assume the role of the Kashmirian—a disguise that grants access and expectation. Methods are at your discretion, with one exception: the Kashmirian himself must be eliminated using an explosive. Precision is essential. No unnecessary attention.\rI’ll leave you to prepare.",
